    content: # PatternFly 5 → 6 Migration Checklist

> **Compiled from**: patternfly.org upgrade guide, pf-codemods README (108 rules),
> patternfly-react source code, npm registry metadata, and GitHub PRs.
>
> **Date**: 2025-05 (PatternFly 6.5.x era)

---

## 1. Package Version Requirements

### Core PatternFly Packages
| Package | v5 | v6 |
|---|---|---|
| `@patternfly/react-core` | `^5.x` | `^6.x` |
| `@patternfly/react-table` | `^5.x` | `^6.x` |
| `@patternfly/react-icons` | `^5.x` | `^6.x` |
| `@patternfly/react-styles` | `^5.x` | `^6.x` |
| `@patternfly/react-tokens` | `^5.x` | `^6.x` |
| `@patternfly/react-charts` | `^7.x` | `^8.x` (import from `/victory`) |
| `@patternfly/react-code-editor` | `^5.x` | `^6.x` |

**Source**: [npmjs.org/@patternfly/react-core](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@patternfly/react-core)

### React Version
| Dependency | `@patternfly/react-core@6.x` | `@patternfly/chatbot@6.x` |
|---|---|---|
| `react` | `^17 \|\| ^18 \|\| ^19` | `^18 \|\| ^19` |
| `react-dom` | `^17 \|\| ^18 \|\| ^19` | `^18 \|\| ^19` |

> **Note**: `@patternfly/react-core` v6.0.0 originally required `^17 || ^18`.
> React 19 support was added later. The `@patternfly/chatbot` package requires
> React 18+ (does NOT support React 17).

**Source**: npm registry peerDependencies for `@patternfly/react-core@6.5.1`, `@patternfly/chatbot@6.6.0`

### Charts (Victory)
Victory is now an **optional peer dependency**. Install separately:
```bash
npm install victory
# OR install specific packages: victory-core, victory-tooltip, etc.
```
**Source**: [pf-codemods: chartsImport-moved](https://github.com/patternfly/pf-codemods)

### @patternfly/chatbot
- Package `@patternfly/chatbot` v6.x depends on `@patternfly/react-core@^6.1.0`
- It replaces the older `@patternfly/virtual-assistant` package
- **Requires React 18+** (no React 17 support)

**Source**: npm registry `@patternfly/chatbot@6.6.0`

---

## 2. Upgrade Steps (Official Order)

1. **Update dependencies** to PF6 versions in `package.json`
2. **Run codemods** (`npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6`)
3. **Run codemods with `--fix`** (`npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6 --fix`)
4. **Run class-name-updater** (`npx @patternfly/class-name-updater --v6 --fix`)
5. **Run tokens-update** codemod for React token updates
6. **Run css-vars-updater** for `.css`/`.scss` files
7. **Remove CSS overrides** — old `--pf-v5-*` variables no longer work
8. **Update breakpoint logic** — PF6 uses `rem` not `px`
9. **Run `data-codemods-cleanup`** once all other codemods are done

**Source**: [patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade](https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade)

---

## 3. CSS / Design Token Changes

### 3.1 Class Name Prefix Change
| v5 | v6 |
|---|---|
| `pf-v5-c-*` | `pf-v6-c-*` |
| `pf-v5-l-*` | `pf-v6-l-*` |
| `pf-v5-u-*` | `pf-v6-u-*` |

**Codemod**: `class-name-updater --v6 --fix` handles this automatically.

### 3.2 CSS Variable / Token Migration
| v5 Format | v6 Format | Example |
|---|---|---|
| `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` | `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` | Global tokens |
| `--pf-v5-global--Color--*` | `--pf-t--global--color--*` | Color tokens |
| `--pf-v5-global--spacer--*` | `--pf-t--global--spacer--*` | Spacer tokens |
| `--pf-v5-c-*` (component vars) | `--pf-v6-c-*` | Component-level vars |

**React tokens** also changed:
| v5 | v6 |
|---|---|
| `global_FontSize_lg` | `t_global_font_size_lg` |
| `global_link_Color_hover` | Manual mapping needed |

> **Important**: There is NO 1:1 mapping for all color tokens. The codemod will
> set unresolvable colors to `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink) so you can
> visually find spots requiring manual attention.

**Codemods**: `tokens-update` (React/.js/.tsx), `css-vars-updater` (.css/.scss)

**Source**: [patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade#3.-review-and-update-variable-and-class-names](https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade)

### 3.3 Breakpoints Changed to `rem`
| Breakpoint | Token | Old (px) | New (rem) |
|---|---|---|---|
| xs | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xs` | 0px | 0rem |
| sm | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--sm` | 576px | 36rem |
| md | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--md` | 768px | 48rem |
| lg | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--lg` | 992px | 62rem |
| xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xl` | 1200px | 75rem |
| 2xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--2xl` | 1450px | 90.625rem |

**Source**: [patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade#4.-update-any-pixel-based-logic-for-breakpoints](https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade)

---

## 4. Removed / Deprecated Components

### 4.1 Fully Removed (from `@patternfly/react-core`)
These were previously deprecated and are now **removed entirely**:

| Component | Replacement |
|---|---|
| **Application Launcher** (deprecated) | Custom menu with `MenuToggle` + `Menu` |
| **Context Selector** (deprecated) | Custom menu |
| **Dropdown** (old deprecated) | New composable `Dropdown` (from `@patternfly/react-core`) |
| **Options Menu** (deprecated) | `Select` (composable) |
| **Page Header** (deprecated) | `Masthead` + `Toolbar` |
| **Select** (old deprecated) | New composable `Select` (from `@patternfly/react-core`) |
| **KebabToggle** (deprecated) | `MenuToggle` with `variant="plain"` |

> **Codemod**: `remove-deprecated-components` — **no autofix**, manual migration required.

**Source**: [pf-codemods: remove-deprecated-components (PR #10345)](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/10345)

### 4.2 Deprecated (moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`)
| Component | Replacement |
|---|---|
| **Chip** / **ChipGroup** | `Label` / `LabelGroup` with `variant="outline"` |
| **Tile** | `Card` |
| **DragDrop** / Droppable / Draggable | `DragDropSort` from `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` |
| **DualListSelector** (old) | New `DualListSelector` (promoted from Next) |
| **Modal** (old, class-based) | New `Modal` (promoted from Next, composable) |

**Codemods**: `chip-deprecated`, `chip-replace-with-label`, `tile-deprecated`, `dragDrop-deprecated`, `modal-deprecated`, `modalNext-promoted`, `dualListSelector-deprecated`, `dualListSelectorNext-promoted`

**Source**: [pf-codemods README](https://github.com/patternfly/pf-codemods)

### 4.3 Text → Content Rename
`Text`, `TextContent`, `TextList`, `TextListItem` are replaced by `Content`.

```jsx
// v5
import { Text, TextContent, TextVariants } from '@patternfly/react-core';
<TextContent><Text component={TextVariants.h1}>Title</Text></TextContent>

// v6
import { Content } from '@patternfly/react-core';
<Content component="h1">Title</Content>
```

**Codemod**: `text-replace-with-content` — autofix available.

**Source**: [pf-codemods: text-replace-with-content (PR #10643)](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/10643)

---

## 5. Component API Changes (Breaking)

### 5.1 Modal — Complete Restructure ⚠️
The old Modal (class-based, single component with `title`/`description`/`actions` props) is **deprecated**. The new Modal is composable:

```jsx
// v5 (old — now deprecated)
import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core';
<Modal title="My Modal" description="desc" actions={[...]} isOpen onClose={fn}>
  Body content
</Modal>

// v6 (new — promoted from Next)
import { Modal, ModalBody, ModalFooter, ModalHeader } from '@patternfly/react-core';
<Modal isOpen onClose={fn} aria-labelledby="modal-title">
  <ModalHeader title="My Modal" description="desc" labelId="modal-title" />
  <ModalBody>Body content</ModalBody>
  <ModalFooter>{/* action buttons */}</ModalFooter>
</Modal>
```

Key differences:
- `title`, `description`, `actions`, `header`, `footer`, `hasNoBodyWrapper`,
  `bodyAriaLabel`, `bodyAriaRole` props are **removed** from Modal
- Use `ModalHeader`, `ModalBody`, `ModalFooter` subcomponents instead
- `variant` values: `'small' | 'medium' | 'large' | 'default'`

**Codemods**: `modal-deprecated` (moves import), `modalNext-promoted` (updates import). **Manual restructuring of Modal usage is required.**

**Source**: [PR #10358](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/10358), [patternfly.org/components/modal](https://www.patternfly.org/components/modal)

### 5.2 Button Changes
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|---|---|---|
| `isActive` → `isClicked` | Prop renamed | `button-rename-isActive` ✅ autofix |
| Icons as children → `icon` prop | For `variant="plain"`, icons must use `icon` prop | `button-moveIcons-icon-prop` ✅ autofix |
| `isDisabled` no longer sets `aria-disabled` | Sets `disabled` attribute instead | Manual test updates |
| Text wrapped in `<span>` | `byText` queries may break — use `byRole` instead | Manual test updates |

**Source**: [PR #10663](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/10663), [PR #9934](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/9934)

### 5.3 Label Changes
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|---|---|---|
| `isOverflowLabel` removed | Use `variant="overflow"` | `label-remove-isOverflowLabel` ✅ autofix |
| `color="cyan"` → `color="teal"` | Color name changed | `colorProps-replaced-colors` ✅ autofix |
| `color="gold"` → `color="yellow"` | Color name changed | `colorProps-replaced-colors` ✅ autofix |
| `icon` prop | Still works — renders left of text. Now also has `status` prop with auto-icon | No migration needed |

**Source**: [PR #10037](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/10037), [PR #10661](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/10661), PF6 source code

### 5.4 MenuToggle Changes
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|---|---|---|
| Icon-only toggles | Pass icons to `icon` prop, NOT as children | `menuToggle-warn-iconOnly-toggle` ⚠️ manual |
| `splitButtonOptions` removed | Restructured | `menuToggle-remove-splitButtonOptions` ✅ autofix |

The `icon` prop on `MenuToggle` accepts `React.ReactNode` and renders before children text.

**Source**: [PR #10097](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/10097), [PR #11096](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/11096), PF6 source code

### 5.5 Dropdown `onSelect` Signature
The v6 composable Dropdown `onSelect` signature is:
```typescript
onSelect?: (event?: React.MouseEvent, value?: DropdownItemProps['value']) => void;
```
This is the same as v5's composable Dropdown. If migrating from the **old deprecated Dropdown**, the signature is completely different (the old one had `(event: React.SyntheticEvent)`).

**Source**: PF6 source code (`Dropdown.tsx`)

### 5.6 ClipboardCopyButton `textId` Deprecated
The `textId` prop on `ClipboardCopyButton` is **deprecated** (marked `@deprecated` in source). It still exists but should not be used. Remove it from your code.

**Source**: [PR #12242](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/12242), PF6 source code

### 5.7 Icon Component — NOT Removed
The `Icon` component **still exists** in `@patternfly/react-core` v6. However:
- For `Button` with `variant="plain"`, icons should use the `icon` prop instead of wrapping in `<Icon>` as children
- For `MenuToggle`, icons should use the `icon` prop

The `Icon` component API is unchanged: `size`, `status`, `isInline`, `isInProgress` props all still work.

**Source**: PF6 source code (`Icon.tsx`)

### 5.8 EmptyState Refactored ⚠️
EmptyState has been significantly restructured. `EmptyStateHeader` is now part of `EmptyState` itself:

```jsx
// v5
import { EmptyState, EmptyStateIcon, EmptyStateHeader, EmptyStateBody } from '@patternfly/react-core';
<EmptyState>
  <EmptyStateHeader titleText="Title" icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={SearchIcon} />} />
  <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>

// v6  
import { EmptyState, EmptyStateBody } from '@patternfly/react-core';
<EmptyState titleText="Title" icon={SearchIcon}>
  <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>
```

**Codemod**: `emptyStateHeader-move-into-emptyState` — partial autofix. **Manual review often needed.**

**Source**: [PR #9947](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/9947), [patternfly.org upgrade guide](https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade)

---

## 6. Other Prop Removals and Renames

| Component | Change | Codemod | Autofix? |
|---|---|---|---|
| **AccordionContent** | `isHidden` removed | `accordionContent-remove-isHidden-prop` | ✅ |
| **AccordionToggle** | `isExpanded` moved to `AccordionItem` | `accordionToggle-move-isExpanded-prop` | ✅ |
| **Avatar** | `border` removed → use `isBordered` | `avatar-replace-border-for-isBordered` | ✅ |
| **Banner** | `variant` removed → `color` or `status` | `banner-replace-variantProp` | ✅ |
| **Card** | `isSelectableRaised`, `isDisabledRaised`, `hasSelectableInput`, `isFlat`, `isRounded` removed | `card-remove-various-props` | ✅ |
| **Checkbox/Radio** | `isLabelBeforeButton` → `labelPosition="start"` | `checkbox-radio-replace-isLabelBeforeButton` | ✅ |
| **DataListAction** | `isPlainButtonAction` removed | `dataListAction-remove-isPlainButtonAction-prop` | ✅ |
| **Drawer** | `colorVariant="light200"` replaced | `drawer-replace-colorVariant-light200` | ✅ |
| **ExpandableSection** | `isActive` removed | `expandableSection-remove-isActive-prop` | ✅ |
| **FormGroup** | `labelIcon` renamed | `formGroup-rename-labelIcon` | ✅ |
| **HelperTextItem** | Various props removed | `helperTextItem-remove-props` | ✅ |
| **JumpLinksItem** | `href` now required | `jumpLinksItem-href-required` | ⚠️ manual |
| **Masthead** | Major structure changes | `masthead-structure-changes` | ⚠️ manual |
| **Nav** | `variant="tertiary"` removed, `theme` removed | `nav-remove-tertiary-variant`, `nav-remove-theme-prop` | ✅ |
| **NavItem** | `hasNavLinkWrapper` removed, use `icon` prop for icons | `navItem-remove-hasNavLinkWrapper-prop` | ✅ |
| **Page** | `header` → `masthead` | `page-rename-header` | ✅ |
| **PageSection** | `variant` values updated, `nav` type removed | `pageSection-update-variant-values` | ✅ |
| **PageSidebar** | `theme` removed | `pageSidebar-remove-theme-prop` | ✅ |
| **Switch** | `labelOff` removed | `switch-remove-labelOff` | ✅ |
| **Tabs** | `isSecondary` renamed; `variant="light300"` removed | `tabs-renamed-isSecondary-prop` | ✅ |
| **Toolbar** | Chip references → Label; various prop removals | `toolbar-replace-chip-instances` | ✅ |

**Source**: [pf-codemods README — 108 rules total](https://github.com/patternfly/pf-codemods)

---

## 7. Import Path Changes

### Charts
```jsx
// v5
import { Chart } from '@patternfly/react-charts';

// v6
import { Chart } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory';
```
**Codemod**: `chartsImport-moved` ✅ autofix

### Deprecated Components
```jsx
// v5 — these were in main package
import { Modal, Chip, DragDrop } from '@patternfly/react-core';

// v6 — moved to deprecated subpath
import { Modal, Chip, DragDrop } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';
```

### React Tokens
```jsx
// v5
import { global_FontSize_lg } from '@patternfly/react-tokens';

// v6 — prefix changed to t_
import { t_global_font_size_lg } from '@patternfly/react-tokens';
```
**Codemod**: `tokens-prefix-with-t` ✅ autofix

---

## 8. Popper / Dropdown / Select Behavior Change

The default `appendTo` for Popper-based components (Dropdown, Select, etc.) changed:
- **v5**: appends to `document.body` (or inline)
- **v6**: Changed default behavior (see codemod `popper-update-appendTo-default`)

**Codemod**: `popper-update-appendTo-default` ⚠️ warning

**Source**: [PR #10675](https://github.com/patternfly/patternfly-react/pull/10675)

---

## 9. Test Failure Patterns

### Button
1. **`aria-disabled` not found**: `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attr, not `aria-disabled`. Update tests that assert `aria-disabled`.
2. **`byText` fails for Button**: Button text is wrapped in `<span>`. Use `byRole('button', { name: 'text' })` instead.

### Select
1. **`byRole` can't find options**: After selection, Popper menu may be `aria-disabled`. Pass `{ hidden: true }` option or use `appendTo="inline"`.

**Source**: [patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade#potential-test-failures](https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade)

---

## 10. Complete Migration Checklist

### Pre-Migration
- [ ] Ensure you're fully on PF5 latest (complete PF4→PF5 upgrade first)
- [ ] Take stock of CSS overrides using `--pf-v5-*` variables
- [ ] Identify usage of deprecated components (old Modal, Chip, Tile, old Dropdown/Select)

### Package Updates
- [ ] Update all `@patternfly/*` packages to v6
- [ ] Install `victory` if using charts
- [ ] Update `@patternfly/chatbot` to v6 (if used) — requires React 18+
- [ ] Run `npm install` / resolve peer dependency warnings

### Automated Migration (Codemods)
- [ ] Run `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6` (dry run)
- [ ] Run `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --fix` (apply fixes)
- [ ] Run class-name-updater: `npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <src> --v6 --fix`
- [ ] Run tokens-update for React tokens
- [ ] Run css-vars-updater for `.css`/`.scss` files
- [ ] Run cleanup: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --only data-codemods-cleanup --fix`
- [ ] Re-run codemods multiple times until clean

### Manual Migration Required
- [ ] **Modal**: Restructure from single-component to composable (`ModalHeader`/`ModalBody`/`ModalFooter`)
- [ ] **EmptyState**: Verify restructured empty states render correctly
- [ ] **Removed components**: Replace old Dropdown/Select/AppLauncher/ContextSelector/OptionsMenu/PageHeader with new composable equivalents
- [ ] **Icon usage**: Move icons from Button/MenuToggle children to `icon` prop
- [ ] **CSS overrides**: Remove/update all `--pf-v5-*` variable overrides
- [ ] **React tokens**: Replace any `t_temp_dev_tbd` placeholders with proper PF6 tokens
- [ ] **Breakpoints**: Update any hardcoded pixel values to rem

### Validation
- [ ] Build succeeds (`npm run build`)
- [ ] Lint passes (`npm run lint-fix`)
- [ ] Unit tests pass (update `aria-disabled` and `byText` assertions)
- [ ] E2E tests pass (update selectors for `pf-v6-*` classes)
- [ ] Visual review — check for hot pink (`--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd`) indicating unresolved tokens
- [ ] i18n strings updated (`npm run i18n`)

