<h3>TypeScript Strict Check Errors (tsc --noEmit)</h3>
<div class="bar-chart">
  <div class="bar-row">
    <div class="bar-label">main (baseline)</div>
    <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill bar-purple" style="width:100%">28</div></div>
