    <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill bar-purple" style="width:100%">28</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="bar-row">
    <div class="bar-label">semver/goose/053126-0138</div>
    <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill bar-purple" style="width:100%">28</div></div>
  </div>
</div>
<p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.85rem;">All 28 errors are in <code>node_modules/</code> (mobx, react-i18next, @patternfly/chatbot, @openshift-console/dynamic-plugin-sdk). No source-level TS errors in any branch.</p>

<h3>ESLint Errors</h3>
<div class="bar-chart">
  <div class="bar-row">
    <div class="bar-label">main (baseline)</div>
    <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill bar-green" style="width:3%">0</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="bar-row">
